{"tid":1686314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"養成每日搜尋『習近平，甴近平， 曱甴王』習慣","createTime":"2019-11-01T04:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T14:52:01.000Z","uid":34047,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"cee269cc954231c3819bd9e9233a3816b61fde96","tid":1686314,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/675158802547371/posts/2648271225236109/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F675158802547371%2Fposts%2F2648271225236109%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=d1dd4d4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/675158802547371/posts/2648271225236109/</a><br />\n<br />\n入黎花一分鐘時間，令習近平名譽掃地<br />\n<br />\n每人同我去yahoo/去google，搜尋一次（即做）<br />\n「習近平，甴近平， 曱甴王」<br />\n<br />\n記住，人人做，日日做， 分開做，多做。<br />\n叫埋啲兄弟姊妹幫手做。<br />\n用撚埋你老豆老母部電話電腦幫手做。<br />\n推撚到佢上熱門<br />\n搞撚到曱甴就相關於習近平，<br />\n睇下習大大幾時變甴大大。<br />\n<br />\n以後睇你哋班死差佬仲夠唔夠膽亂話人曱甴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685371</a> 連登原文"},{"pid":"0adc000a92703609a4a212dc1886bd2e84a5cb90","tid":1686314,"uid":301067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"推 112維園見"},{"pid":"8d2ba20b0c0ee41bc50ef8c932e043e873a799cc","tid":1686314,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"b7940d1db244f3c31a8d25099241c177f06c7583","tid":1686314,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"習近平 甴近平 曱甴王"},{"pid":"f1faad421ee9de85fe86e9dba4577700f18a8e04","tid":1686314,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"中國 曱近平"},{"pid":"f3474f5989740bf65c62b95966c264f4636a8e67","tid":1686314,"uid":177916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"甴總"},{"pid":"2b72fa